items.content_text:
### HTTP

*   [http-kit (‚≠ê2.5k)](https://github.com/http-kit/http-kit) : Simple, high-performance event-driven HTTP client and server
*   [ring (‚≠ê3.8k)](https://github.com/ring-clojure/ring) : HTTP server abstraction
*   [kvlt (‚≠ê69)](https://github.com/nervous-systems/kvlt) : Uniform, asychronous client interface for HTTP across JVM / Node / browsers
